title: Over 26 Hours of Offbeat Christmas Music Mix CDs
description:
For 15 years, over 22 discs, I have been making holiday mixes and original music. I am eager to share these efforts with the world.

Many of these songs have been shortened, otherwise altered, and designed to flow into one another. As such it's not a great way to find definitive versions of songs. However, if you're looking to get off the beaten path of holiday music I have a very deep rabbit hole for you!
